### Overall Layout (Design Overview)
- **Left Side**: Ek badi background image (dark overlay ke saath) + logo + tagline (e.g., “This is not a real online service…”)
- **Right Side**: White background mein sign-up form
- Form ke upar heading: “Create your account” or similar
- Form fields vertically stacked
- Bottom mein “Already have an account? Log in” link
- Modern, clean look with subtle shadows aur nice typography

### Form Fields (Exactly jaise design mein)

| Field / Section                  | Type                  | Notes / Requirements |
|----------------------------------|-----------------------|----------------------|
| **First Name**                   | Text input            | Required |
| **Last Name**                    | Text input            | Required |
| **Email**                        | Email input           | Required, use `type="email"` |
| **Phone Number**                 | Tel input             | Use `type="tel"` |
| **Password**                     | Password input        | Required |
| **Confirm Password**             | Password input        | Required, match with password |
| **Create Account**               | Submit button         | Big green/blue button |
| **Already have an account?**     | Link                  | “Log in” text as link |

### HTML Structure Suggestion (Recommended)

```html
<div class="container">
  <!-- Left Sidebar -->
  <div class="sidebar">
    <img src="background.jpg" alt="">
    <div class="overlay">
      <img src="logo.png" alt="Odin Logo">
      <p>Some catchy text...</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right Form Area -->
  <div class="form-area">
    <h1>Create your account</h1>
    <form>
      <div class="form-row">
        <label>First Name</label>
        <input type="text" required>
      </div>
      <!-- Similarly for other fields -->
      
      <button type="submit">Create Account</button>
    </form>
    <p>Already have an account? <a href="#">Log in</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
```

### CSS Key Techniques (Jo Is Project Mein Use Hote Hain)

| Technique                        | Kya Use Karo?                                      | Why Important? |
|----------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|----------------|
| **Flexbox**                      | Main container ko split karne ke liye              | Left image + right form side-by-side |
| **Background Image + Overlay**   | `background-image` + dark semi-transparent layer   | Text readable banane ke liye |
| **Form Styling**                 | `padding`, `border-radius`, `box-shadow`, `:focus` | Clean & modern look |
| **Custom Properties**            | `--primary-color`, `--spacing` etc.                | Easy to maintain |
| **Responsive**                   | Media queries (mobile pe stack ho jaye)            | Good practice |
| **Password Match Check**         | JavaScript se (optional but recommended)           | Real validation feel |
| **Error States**                 | `:invalid`, `:valid`, custom red border            | UX improvement |

